        <section id="product-list-optimized" class="mb-12 p-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral border-b-4 border-primary pb-2 mb-6">4. UI/UX 產品卡片展示範例 (高信任度設計)</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
